  CLEAR_CART: "CLEAR_CART",
  ADD_CART_TO_FIRESTORE_START: "ADD_CART_TO_FIRESTORE_START",
  FETCH_CART_ITEMS_FROM_FIRESTORE_START:
    "FETCH_CART_ITEMS_FROM_FIRESTORE_START",
  FETCH_CART_ITEMS_FROM_FIRESTORE_SUCCESS:
    "FETCH_CART_ITEMS_FROM_FIRESTORE_SUCCESS",
  FETCH_CART_ITEMS_FROM_FIRESTORE_FAILURE:
